file_content.text: We could use more firepower.
Maybe we can find something to clear a path through this battle.
My sister's sending everything she has at us.
More enemies closing in!
They're coming from all sides!
We must drive the invaders back to Zakuul!
Wave after wave... They just keep coming!
I don't know how long our troops can last against this onslaught.
Vaylin's pulling out all the stops.
She won't stop until Odessen is wiped out.
Hurry! We can't lose the Gravestone!
They can't hold the Gravestone much longer! Come on!
Can Torian hold out long enough for us to reach him?
We're getting close.
Torian's a good kid. We won't let him down.
Even a Mandalorian can't survive this without help.
How long do you think Vette can hold her position?
We're almost there.
Long enough for us to get there... I hope.
He's Mandalorian. He'll keep fighting until the end.
I hope Torian is still alive.
We're almost there. I hope we're not too late.
He's Mandalorian. He will fight until the bitter end.
I hope we're not too late.
Vette's tougher than she looks. She'll survive this.
This is taking too long. Vette can't hold out forever!
We have to keep moving. Vette needs our help.
She's a good kid. We won't let her down.
Hold the lines. Enemy reinforcements coming in from the west.
Oggurobb's bringing some new toys for the troops. Let's light the enemy up!
Sana-Rae is leading our Force-users in a counter strike against the enemy flank.
The south perimeter has been breached! Fall back to the rally point!
Oggurobb's position is overrun! Send in troops to cover their retreat!
Sana-Rae's forces are being pushed back. Reinforcements heading her way.
We're taking heavy losses. Pulling back to set up a defensive perimeter.
Torian died a Mandalorian's death. Clan Cadera will remember his name.
Picking up an enemy comm signal in our area, Commander. Slicing into the feed.
Picking up an enemy comm signal in your area, Commander. Patching it through...
Cut off the retreat and pin the Alliance forces in the valley. Burn Odessen, and bring me the ashes. I want them for my garden.
If Vaylin blocks this passage, our troops are trapped! We have to break through their lines!
If Vaylin blocks that passage, our troops are trapped! You have to break through their lines.
All clear, Commander. Valley's secured.
All clear in your area, Commander. The valley's secured.
Father's pet. I was just talking about you.
What's the matter, Vaylin? Too scared to come face me in person?
I will chew up your friends, and grind your precious Alliance into paste. When I finally hunt you down, you'll beg me to end your suffering.
Your whole family's on Odessen. Valkorion, Arcann, even Senya. Stop playing games, and come have your revenge!
Valkorion's all that remains of your family. If you want revenge, come and claim it!
Argh!!
Nice work. If that doesn't lure her down here, nothing will.
Nice work. If that doesn't lure her down there, nothing will.
